author: Nexcell Pride
text:
A great streaming ever... And a great adventure. :_きゅん:
Riding on a Skull horse (Undead) and fighting against zombies, but with a tragedy included: at 1:53:03 Konta seems poisoned by a toxic zombie and later commited suicide at fire. :_あせり:
At 1:55:45 we felt the sadness about losing more than a mascot, a best friend. :_ちょうちょ:

But leaving that sad event, it seems Rushia-hime is going to colonize a place... Possibly she's going to found a city later.
But the surprise begins at 2:10:01 with 2 Kontas (Foxes) inside a house. And suddenly... The rest is just telling itself. :_るんるん:

Possibly Rushia would have a fox farm later... Or who knows...

Supaachato Orei Time was short this time with only 34 minutes length, but at least after ending was performed :_ちょうちょ:
